Ali the Barman owns The Asp & Snake Bar in Pollnivneach. Other than serving fine drinks to his thirsty customers, he may be assisting players with The Feud quest.

He sells a variety of drinks. The drinks are beer, whisky, wine, vodka, brandy and grog.

The NPC's name has been changed from "Ali The barman" to "Ali the Barman".

Trivia[edit | edit source]

  • Like all the people in Pollnivneach, his name is Ali.
  • During The Feud, he informs the players that Drunken Ali has gone to the bathroom, which brings him to the fact that there are no toilets seen in Gielinor.
